7107-7117 Juniper Valley Road, north side, between 71st and 72nd Streets, showing in the foreground (7107-7109) the Ed. Morrell house. Some owners were R. Morrell 1852, Mrs. Morrell 1873, and E. Morrell or E. Monell in 1891. (See 1891 Queens Atlas.) This is a set of two views showing the front and rear of the house.

1922.
View 2: March 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
